  "Description": "CALLED BY:          IdsEdwCustSvcFBalSeq\n\nPROCESSING:\n                  This is where the actual balancing takes place and the Source and Target tables are compared on the specified column to see if there are any discrepancies\n\nMODIFICATIONS:\nDeveloper                          Date                 Project/Altiris #                Change Description                             Development Project    Code Reviewer            Date Reviewed\n----------------------------------      -------------------    -----------------------------------    ---------------------------------------------------------      ----------------------------------   ---------------------------------    -------------------------   \nParikshith Chada               08/29/2007          3264                              Originally Programmed                           devlEDW10              Steph Goddard            10/21/2007                \n\nBhupinder Kaur                12/06/2013          5114                               Rewrite in Parallel                            EnterpriseWhseDevl       Jag Yelavarthi               2014-02-25\n\nAnnotations:\nRows with Failed Comparison on Specified columns\nDetail file for on-call to research errors\nJob: EdwEdwBCustSvcFBal\nFile checked later for rows and email to on-call\nCopy stage used to remove duplicates and create one record for the Notification file.\nPull all the Missing Records from\nCUST_SVC_ F\nB_CUST_SVC_F"
